# textdomain: mcl_armor

This is a piece of equippable armor which reduces the amount of damage you receive.=To je kos nosljivega oklepa, ki zmanjša količino prejete škode.
To equip it, put it on the corresponding armor slot in your inventory menu.=Če ga želite obleči, ga postavite v ustrezno režo za oklep v meniju inventarja.
Sentry=Stražar
Dune=Sipina
Coast=Obala
Wild=Divjina
Tide=Plima
Ward=Varuh
Vex=Bes
Rib=Rebro
Snout=Rilec
Eye=Oko
Spire=Konica
Silence=Tišina
Wayfinder=Iskalec poti
